name: Barry Deck
biography:
Barry Deck grew up in American suburb.
Enrolled at California Institute of the Arts in 1987
Designs type, photo-illustrations, graphic design, and design production.
This type Template Gothic, a huge success and even used for Time Warner's 1991 annual report.
Feature in Bierut, Michael "American Gothic" ID v. 41 (Jan./Fen. 1994): 43.
